openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: recursive test
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:8000/'
paths:
  /ping:
    get:
      operationId: ping
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/B'
components:
  schemas:
    B:
      type: object
      required: ["message2"]
      properties:
        message:
          type: string
        message2:
          type: string
        details:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/B'
